{"tid":2175891,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"差點七天後回家！騎車半路老虎追上來","createTime":"2020-08-26T17:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T16:28:15.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7635e4d2ef1ee191f85a0bc73c7c8834b855958b","tid":2175891,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T17:53:00.000Z","msg":"在台灣，騎車的人大部分都有被野狗追的經驗，不過日前在印度喀拉拉邦的瓦亞納德縣，有兩位男子騎車經過野生動物保護區時，突然有一隻老虎從草叢中竄出來，瘋狂地追逐著他們，好險在機車騎士的快速行駛下，得以拉開與老虎的差距，這一幕驚險畫面被坐在後座的人拍下後，分享到網路上，引起網友一陣瘋傳，看見老虎窮追不捨的樣子，實在是太可怕了！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mXtnT1XCWPQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmXtnT1XCWPQ&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=e126feac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mXtnT1XCWPQ</a><br />\n<br />\n有網友認為，好險機車駕駛臨危不亂，在這種時候還能穩住龍頭，將老虎甩在後方，不過也有人說：「如果人類不入侵到老虎的地盤，其實牠們也不會找上門。」，只能說這一次兩人能順利脫逃，真的是有驚無險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=565228\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D565228&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=d49e92c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D565228&h=87f19903\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=565228</a>"},{"pid":"04e647312925723cbf56abdd65af48e0429b6dfe","tid":2175891,"uid":191453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:28:09.000Z","msg":"老虎：仆街你跌咗野呀!喂!喂!仆街越叫越走!?"},{"pid":"250df60b7af60f3f258dacddf25d466a856397bc","tid":2175891,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T16:28:15.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"green\"></span>"}]}